================================================================================
Pattern attribution (no code copied)
================================================================================

Several Odysseus skills and specialists encode workflow patterns originally
described in willchen96/mike (https://github.com/willchen96/mike), which is
licensed under AGPL-3.0. The Odysseus artifacts are pattern extractions
(prompts, structural workflows, output schemas), not code copies; no AGPL-3.0
source code from mike has been incorporated into Odysseus. The following
Odysseus artifacts cite mike as their reference implementation:

  - skills/legal/tabular-review/
  - skills/legal/clause-extraction-presets/
  - skills/legal/docx-tracked-changes/
  - skills/legal/docx-generation/
  - agents/specialists/corporate/cp-checklist-generator.md
  - agents/specialists/corporate/credit-agreement-summarizer.md
  - agents/specialists/corporate/sha-summarizer.md
  - agents/specialists/commercial/tabular-reviewer.md

If, in a future commit, any AGPL-3.0 code from mike is incorporated into
Odysseus, that code will be segregated into a separately-licensed sub-package,
and this NOTICE will be updated to reflect the dual-license posture.
